Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马怎么淋成个落汤鸡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半路上下起了大雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  总之先把衣服脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  把热水准备起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:49.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在态度上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真舒服啊
