Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你可可  是热的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真会添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是全套的国王待遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了千秋  借套衣服给我穿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么态度啊  求人的方法就这么一种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最会装撒娇的小女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  衣服还要等上一段时间才会干
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就交给我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来纠正冬马的小女儿脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？嗯…那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  藤冈什么时候来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:01:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  藤冈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  快把衣服借我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直这样下去  有点儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋衣服借来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是故意找麻烦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来夏树昨天这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两把刷子嘛  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  看我这招  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  把那个类似手柄的东西给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了冬马  再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  看招  看招  看招…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  男子汉的恩仇都要双倍奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身为男子汉  我要从你那儿把衣服夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？只因为你是女生  没衣服穿感到很为难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了冬马   我的衣服借你穿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋啊  你就借衣服给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就  不  借
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊  突然下起雨来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快借给我  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不借就不借
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我宰了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了  千秋大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借衣服给我吧  我知错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好孩子  还是会求人的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我房间来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好求你就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别当没事儿人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要注意态度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香都欢迎你了  你这什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了  藤冈也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快脱了快脱了  总之先泡个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是何事啊？
