Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这糖真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟宝石一样  红艳艳的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些天然色素是提取虫子的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点儿  内田
